<ul>
<li><a href="/wiki/Ituri_conflict" title="Ituri conflict">Ituri conflict</a>, ongoing conflict in northeastern DRC between the <a href="/wiki/Lendu" title="Lendu">Lendu</a> and <a href="/wiki/Hema_(ethnicity)" title="Hema (ethnicity)" class="mw-redirect">Hema</a> ethnic groups</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Kivu_conflict" title="Kivu conflict">Kivu conflict</a>, ongoing conflict between the DRC army and rebels led by <a href="/wiki/Laurent_Nkunda" title="Laurent Nkunda">Laurent Nkunda</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Living_in_Emergency:_Stories_of_Doctors_Without_Borders" title="Living in Emergency: Stories of Doctors Without Borders">Living in Emergency</a> (<a href="/wiki/Documentary_film" title="Documentary film">documentary film</a> about the work of <a href="/wiki/M%C3%A9decins_Sans_Fronti%C3%A8res" title="Médecins Sans Frontières">Médecins Sans Frontières</a> in DR Congo)</li>
</ul>
