<li>Thomas Turner. <a href="http://www.fpif.org/briefs/vol5/v5n10congo.html" class="external text" title="http://www.fpif.org/briefs/vol5/v5n10congo.html" rel="nofollow">"War in the Congo"</a> at Foreign Policy in Focus, April 2000</li>
<li><a href="http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/world/africa/573051.stm" class="external text" title="http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/world/africa/573051.stm" rel="nofollow">BBC: timeline of war</a>, <i>BBC News</i> <span class="mw-formatted-date" title="2001-01-17"><a href="/wiki/January_17" title="January 17">17 January</a> <a href="/wiki/2001" title="2001">2001</a></span></li>
